  "description": {
    "zh": "小伙子，你现在有空吗？国外有一个大客户对一些高价值的医疗设备感兴趣。与其把它们留在这里任混蛋们蹂躏，不如选择相信客户们会好好利用这些设备，你懂的。如果你能找到我需要的工具，我会很感谢你。拿着，这是所需工具的清单。",
    "en": "Young man, are you busy at the moment? An interested party from abroad, from behind the barricades, took an interest in a big batch of valuable medical equipment. I think they will find a better use if, instead of the scum here, you understand me. I would be extremely grateful if you could find the required tools for me. Here, take this. This is the list containing all the needed tools."
  },
